  <h1>	What makes us different?</h1>
  <div class="col360">
	<p>Design and Language are the lifeblood of Second Road. The deliberate fusion of these two distinct yet complementary systems acts as catalyst to liberate creative thinking and cohere diverse communities.</p> 
	
	<p>We can’t avoid complexity. The challenge is how we respond to it. Second Road relishes the big, wicked problems that live in a complex landscape. Working with our clients we take a whole-of-system approach to harness ambiguity. At the core of our approach is the art and science that reside in design and language. We use these elements to carve creative, pragmatic pathways through complexity.</p> 
	
	<p>The elegance of language is its ability to unlock meaning, create clarity and convey relevance. The genius of design is its capacity to discover, invent and transform. Together, language and design turns complexity into opportunity.</p> 
